0484 DISP_EXP_VAL       ; Position in display buffer to write player experience points (text- 10 chars, left justified)
0499 DISP_HP_SEP_CHAR   ; Position in display buffer to write ':' (HP < Max) or '=' (HP = Max) (text - 1 char)
049A DISP_HP_VAL        ; Position in display buffer to write current HP (text - 5 chars, left justified)
04A1 DISP_LOC_DESC      ; Position in display buffer to write location description (text - 40 chars, left justified)
